{"tid":384004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成世人都唔知自己想點","createTime":"2017-09-02T03:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T02:15:15.000Z","uid":139272,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a75fa51cb97eb130b6dd773e01763f7a0d58a397","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"最近見工比人問:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你有咩興趣?」</span><br />\n<br />\n明明一條咁易答既題目<br />\n我都要諗左成幾十秒<br />\n最後先彈左句: 閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (明明自己都係一般興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n由細到大我都係習慣滿足人地期望<br />\n為左令父母唔洗擔心，讀書要好成績唔去玩<br />\n為左可以起社會生存，明知無興趣既major都要照讀<br />\n為左要識到多D朋友，就算玩既活動無興趣都要跟機<br />\n平時得閒無野做就淨係識打下機<br />\n玩咁多年都仲係玩緊同一隻game<br />\n見到身邊有朋友無論以前點差都好，而家都搵到自己興趣努力發展<br />\n而我就仲起度一日過得一日咁<br />\n得閒就搵朋友玩<br />\n想比個目標自己去做都難<br />\n因為我真係唔知自己中意咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有無巴絲都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f7373449ffc6fb28651e0c3a379368723412e9","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d6cbe796e368358965f50ab53100279e36728b","tid":384004,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"有錢就知了"},{"pid":"2531547b6a7c7da6a3c7830467296b906a7ea4e0","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢就知了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最弊有錢可能都唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7194a0083542275a59e01dfa9b43bc8e8c79c7e","tid":384004,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"怕醜"},{"pid":"2cc161db716430e1aef17876852350b96375fe7a","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怕醜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣都係其中之一啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea4948ad33ef07c110cb05474279a1e81e9c5b4","tid":384004,"uid":7915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"人生目標係搵到目標"},{"pid":"9c44bcca2dd4daa8e21174dea5717fb5ae805c87","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生目標係搵到目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩啊! 巴打有無目標分享下? 睇下有無得跟跟機參考下"},{"pid":"7977bc9463e816fd2364f1a8b9de53e6083819d9","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"大家有咩興趣多架? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比小毒毒參考下都好啊"},{"pid":"dd48abe22751453d00dd6673968822938cd23f8a","tid":384004,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"整嘢食<br />\n玩車"},{"pid":"30f52f558f5f4f5ddce26d77d53b30cfedbb0e5b","tid":384004,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整嘢食<br />\n玩車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打整野食?好仔加分條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整咩野食多啊?"},{"pid":"fcbea0ac9a68da4eb3e2481c88d17bb7b146a62d","tid":384004,"uid":121885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"見工前唔識諗定d同工作有關既興趣？ 擺明加分位黎wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cd61b30d7472ba9d90fa4d5b0fc597d7717e00","tid":384004,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"咁你鍾唔鍾意女人"},{"pid":"c3064b4d60d34fe40c59f7a7a28ab48733d25c95","tid":384004,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"我直接答冇<img src=\"/assets/face